profile:
D. Roy Contracting company is based out of Ottawa, Ontario.
We have been in business for over a decade. 
We are an energetic team of general contractors with the goal to help improve the look and feel of your home. 
Our mission is to provide the best quality work in a timely fashion with an affordable price to ensure an all-around great customer experience. 
All jobs include a limited warranty because we stand behind what we do.
